answers.body_markdown:
I believe this is what you are looking for, add this snippet to your theme/Child theme&#39;s functions.php file. Change &#39;post&#39; in the second line to the post type name you wish to add custom field support for.


    function add_custom_field_support_for_cpt() {
        add_post_type_support( &#39;post&#39;, &#39;custom-fields&#39; );
    }
    add_action( &#39;init&#39;, &#39;add_custom_field_support_for_cpt&#39; );

for further reference check out the the WordPress documentation at [Function Reference/add post type support][1] 

Hope that helps. 

  [1]: https://codex.wordpress.org/Function_Reference/add_post_type_support

